title: Rich Stuffed chicken dish with beans
directions: Heat a frying pan without oil or butter and fry the bacon in 3 min. From. Add the onion and mushroom mixture and cook 4 min., Stirring over high heat. Meanwhile, cut the chicken breast fillets into pieces.
Add the chopped tomatoes, kale, sauce and wrap the chicken and cook 4 min. On high heat cooking. Stir occasionally. Add the bean mixture chickpeas, brown & white beans and cook 2 min. With.
ingredients: 740 g bean mixture chickpeas, kidney beans and white
